Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:08.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}君の横顔が見詰めているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}次の季節だっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}分かってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}痛いくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:25.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}反射的に笑顔を作る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:32.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}曖昧な線　揺曳な隙まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:38.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}無邪気なあざとさで夢を繋いだの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}噓だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:49.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}純度だけは固くて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}ほら　眩しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:56.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}涙　ダイヤモンド
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:22:01.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}きっと終わりが始まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:08.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}ずっと忘れない季節でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:08.87,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我凝视着你的侧颜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.53,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是因为我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}那是下一个季节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}反射般的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:25.05,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我作出让自己心痛的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:32.15,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}暧昧的线在摇荡的缝隙间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:38.56,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我用天真的小聪明延续着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.96,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}尽是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.85,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}尽是伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:49.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}唯有纯度坚固如昔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}看 那耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:56.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}泪水的钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:22:01.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}结局一定开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:08.81,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\}那一定是永生难忘的季节吧
